<HEADLINE> Shanxi Province Improving Life of Vocational School Teachers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TAIYUAN, August 7 (Xinhua) -- North China's Shanxi Province has
made an effort to improve living and working conditions of
vocational education teachers.
</P>
<P>
To promote vocational education and reward outstanding teaching
staff, the local education department has set up a number of
foundations to provide apartments for vocational school teachers.
</P>
<P>
It has also raised their salaries, and developed health
insurance and retirement benefits for them in recent years.
</P>
<P>
Many senior technicians from local enterprises have been
employed by vocational schools, and are playing an important role
in vocational education.
</P>
