and Service Companies, during April-June this year software
exports grossed 13.6 billion rupees (about 389 million US
dollars), up from 8.2 billion rupees (about 234 million dollars)
in the corresponding quarter of the previous year.
</P>
<P>
The study said the year 2000 date conversion projects have made
useful contribution to the growth of software exports.
</P>
<P>
India has already bagged 700 million dollars worth of orders in
the year 2000 conversion projects, it said.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
