<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 7 (Xinhua) -- The People's Liberation Army
(PLA) forces in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR)
have set up a border checkpoint in the Cassino Lines to check the
garrison's personnel and vehicles crossing the border.
</P>
<P>
