<HEADLINE> China's New Municipality Attracting More Overseas Investment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHONGQING, August 7 (Xinhua/OANA) -- Japan's Isuzu Motors,
Thailand's Chia Tai Group, and a British multinational have
decided to spend 120 million US dollars more in Chongqing, part of
