Air New Zealand, up 2 cents to 307 cents. All Fletcher stocks also
closed higher with Building rising 2 cents to 440 cents, Energy 8
cents to 545 cents, Forests 2 cents to 196 cents and Paper 5 cents
to 345 cents.
</P>
<P>
There were 56 rises and 43 falls.  
